                local match = text:sub(i):match("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" .. c .. c)
                if match then
                    curString = "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

"
                    skip = i + #match
                    arguments[#arguments + 1] = match:sub(2, -2)
                else
                    curString = curString .. c
                end
            elseif c == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" and curString ~= "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                arguments[#arguments + 1] = curString
                curString = "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

"
            else
                if not (c == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" and curString == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

") then curString = curString .. c end
            end
        end
    end

    if curString ~= "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then arguments[#arguments + 1] = curString end
    return arguments
end

local function combineBracketArgs(args)
    local result = {}
    local buffer
    for _, a in ipairs(args) do
        if buffer then
            buffer = buffer .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" .. a
            if a:sub(-1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                result[#result + 1] = buffer
                buffer = nil
            end
        elseif a:sub(1, 1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" and a:sub(-1) ~= "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
            buffer = a
            if a:sub(-1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                result[#result + 1] = buffer
                buffer = nil
            end
        else
            result[#result + 1] = a
        end
    end

    if buffer then result[#result + 1] = buffer end
    return result
end

local function isPlaceholder(arg)
    return isstring(arg) and arg:sub(1, 1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" and arg:sub(-1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

"
end

if SERVER then
    function lia.command.run(client, command, arguments)
        local commandTbl = lia.command.list[command:lower()]
        if commandTbl then
            local results = {commandTbl.onRun(client, arguments or {})}
            hook.Run("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", client, command, arguments or {}, results)
            local result = results[1]
            if isstring(result) then
                if IsValid(client) then
                    if result:sub(1, 1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                        client:notifyInfoLocalized(result:sub(2), unpack(results, 2))
                    else
                        client:notifyErrorLocalized(result)
                    end
                else
                    print(result)
                end
            end
        end
    end

    function lia.command.parse(client, text, realCommand, arguments)
        if realCommand or utf8.sub(text, 1, 1) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
            local match = realCommand or text:lower():match("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
            if not match then
                local post = string.Explode("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", text)
                local len = string.len(post[1])
                match = utf8.sub(post[1], 2, len)
            end

            match = match:lower()
            local command = lia.command.list[match]
            if command then
                if not arguments then arguments = lia.command.extractArgs(text:sub(#match + 3)) end
                local fields = command.arguments or {}
                if IsValid(client) and client:IsPlayer() and #fields > 0 then
                    local tokens = combineBracketArgs(arguments)
                    local missing = {}
                    local prefix = {}
                    for i, field in ipairs(fields) do
                        local arg = tokens[i]
                        if not arg or isPlaceholder(arg) then
                            if not field.optional then missing[#missing + 1] = field.name end
                        else
                            prefix[#prefix + 1] = arg
                        end
                    end

                    if #missing > 0 then
                        net.Start("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
                        net.WriteString(match)
                        net.WriteTable(missing)
                        net.WriteTable(prefix)
                        net.Send(client)
                        return true
                    end
                end

                lia.command.run(client, match, arguments)
                if not realCommand then lia.log.add(client, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", text) end
            else
                if IsValid(client) then
                    client:notifyErrorLocalized("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
                else
                    lia.information(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        frame:SetTitle("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        frame:SetSize(frameW, frameH)

            derma.SkinHook("

Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", frame)
        scroll:Dock(FILL)
        scroll:DockMargin(10, 40, 10, 10)
        surface.SetFont("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        local controls = {}
        local watchers = {}
        local validate
        for name, data in pairs(fields) do
            local fieldType = data.type
            local optional = data.optional
            local options = data.options
            local filter = data.filter
            local panel = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", scroll)
            panel:Dock(TOP)
            panel:DockMargin(0, 0, 0, 5)
            panel:SetTall(70)

            local textW = select(1, surface.GetTextSize(L(data.description or name)))
            local ctrl
            if fieldType == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                ctrl = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

                ctrl:SetValue(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", panel)
            else
                ctrl = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

                ctrl:SetFont("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
            end

            local label = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", panel)
            label:SetFont("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")

            label:SizeToContents()
            panel.PerformLayout = function(_, w, h)
                local ctrlH = 30
                ctrl:SetTall(ctrlH)
                local ctrlW = w * 0.7
                local totalW = textW + 10 + ctrlW
                local xOff = (w - totalW) / 2
                label:SetPos(xOff, (h - label:GetTall()) / 2)
                ctrl:SetPos(xOff + textW + 10, (h - ctrlH) / 2)
                ctrl:SetWide(ctrlW)
            end

            controls[name] = {
                ctrl = ctrl,
                type = fieldType,
                optional = optional
            }

            watchers[#watchers + 1] = function()
                local oldValue = ctrl.OnValueChange
                function ctrl:OnValueChange(...)
                    if oldValue then oldValue(self, ...) end
                    validate()
                end

                local oldText = ctrl.OnTextChanged
                function ctrl:OnTextChanged(...)
                    if oldText then oldText(self, ...) end
                    validate()
                end

                local oldChange = ctrl.OnChange
                function ctrl:OnChange(...)
                    if oldChange then oldChange(self, ...) end
                    validate()
                end

                local oldSelect = ctrl.OnSelect
                function ctrl:OnSelect(...)
                    if oldSelect then oldSelect(self, ...) end
                    validate()
                end
            end
        end

        local buttons = vgui.Create("

            for _, data in pairs(controls) do

                    else
                        filled = ctl:GetValue() ~= nil and ctl:GetValue() ~= "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

"
                    end

                    if not filled then
                        submit:SetEnabled(false)
                        return
                    end
                end
            end

            submit:SetEnabled(true)
        end

        for _, fn in ipairs(watchers) do
            fn()
        end

        validate()
        local cancel = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", buttons)
        cancel:Dock(RIGHT)
        cancel:SetWide(270)
        cancel:SetText(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        cancel.DoClick = function() frame:Remove() end
        submit.DoClick = function()
            local args = {}
            if prefix then table.Add(args, prefix) end
            for _, info in pairs(controls) do
                local ctl = info.ctrl
                local typ = info.type
                local val
                if typ == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" or typ == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                    local _, dataVal = ctl:GetSelected()
                    val = dataVal or ctl:GetValue()
                elseif typ == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" then
                    val = ctl:GetChecked()
                else
                    val = ctl:GetValue()
                end

                args[#args + 1] = val ~= "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" and val or nil
            end

            RunConsoleCommand("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" .. cmdKey .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

" .. table.concat(args, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

"))
            frame:Remove()
        end
    end

    function lia.command.send(command, ...)
        net.Start("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        net.WriteString(command)
        net.WriteTable({...})
        net.SendToServer()
    end
end

        for _, fn in ipairs(files) do

Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        local validCount = 0
        local invalidCount = 0
        for _, fileName in ipairs(files) do
            if string.EndsWith(fileName, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

") then
                local data = file.Read(baseDir .. fileName, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
                if data then
                    local success, soundData = pcall(pon.decode, data)
                    if success and soundData then
                        validCount = validCount + 1
                    else
                        invalidCount = invalidCount + 1
                    end
                end
            end
        end

        LocalPlayer():ChatPrint(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        local removedCount = 0
        for _, fileName in ipairs(files) do
            if string.EndsWith(fileName, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
                if not data then
                    file.Delete(baseDir .. fileName)
                    removedCount = removedCount + 1
                else
                    local success, soundData = pcall(pon.decode, data)
                    if not success or not soundData then
                        file.Delete(baseDir .. fileName)
                        removedCount = removedCount + 1
                    end
                end
            end
        end

        LocalPlayer():ChatPrint(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

")
        if #files == 0 then return end
        LocalPlayer():ChatPrint(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

") then LocalPlayer():ChatPrint(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\commands.lua

", function()
        local files = findImagesRecursive(baseDir)
        if not files or #files == 0 then return end
        local f = vgui.Create("

"[<>\"
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then return false, L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") end
        return
    end

    local url = u or lia.webimage.stored[n] and lia.webimage.stored[n].url
    local flg = flags or lia.webimage.stored[n] and lia.webimage.stored[n].flags
    if not url or url == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" then
        if cb then cb(nil, false, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") end
        return
    end

    local isValidURL, validationError = validateURL(url)
    if not isValidURL then
        if cb then cb(nil, false, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. validationError) end
        return
    end

    if isstring(url) then urlMap[url] = n end
    cache[n] = nil
    local savePath = baseDir .. n
    local function finalize(fromCache)
        local m = buildMaterial(savePath, flg)
        cache[n] = m
        if cb then cb(m, fromCache) end
        if not fromCache and not stats.downloadedImages[n] then
            stats.downloadedImages[n] = true
            stats.downloaded = stats.downloaded + 1
            hook.Run("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", n, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. savePath)
        end
    end

    local cleanName = n:gsub("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
    local extension = nil
    for _, ext in ipairs({"
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

"}) do
        local testPath = baseDir .. cleanName .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. ext
        if file.Exists(testPath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
            savePath = testPath
            finalize(true)
            return
        end
    end

    http.Fetch(url, function(b)
        if string.lower(string.sub(b, 2, 4)) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" then
            extension = "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

"
        elseif string.lower(string.sub(b, 7, 10)) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" or string.lower(string.sub(b, 7, 10)) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

"
        end

        if not extension then
            if cb then cb(nil, false, L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. extension
        if file.Exists(savePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
            local existingSize = file.Size(savePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
            if existingSize == #b then
                finalize(true)
                return
            end
        end

        local dirPath = savePath:match("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
        if dirPath then
            ensureDir(dirPath)
        else
            ensureDir(baseDir)
        end

        file.Write(savePath, b)
        finalize(false)
    end, function(e)
        for _, ext in ipairs({"
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

"}) do
            local testPath = baseDir .. cleanName .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. ext
            if file.Exists(testPath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
                savePath = testPath
                finalize(true)
                return
            end
        end

        if cb then cb(nil, false, e) end
    end)
end

function lia.webimage.register(n, u, cb, flags)
    lia.webimage.stored[n] = {
        url = u,
        flags = flags
    }

    lia.webimage.download(n, u, cb, flags)
end

function lia.webimage.get(n, flags)
    local key = urlMap[n] or n
    if cache[key] then return cache[key] end
    local savePath = baseDir .. key
    if file.Exists(savePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
        local m = buildMaterial(savePath, flags)
        cache[key] = m
        return m
    end
end

local origMaterial = Material
function Material(p, ...)
    local flags = select(1, ...)
    if isstring(p) then
        if p:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. baseDir .. n, flags)
        elseif p:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
            local webPath = p:gsub("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
            local mat = lia.webimage.get(webPath, flags)
            if mat then return mat end
            return origMaterial("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. baseDir .. webPath, flags)
        elseif p:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. baseDir .. webPath, flags)
        else
            local mat = lia.webimage.get(p, flags)
            if mat then return mat end
        end
    end
    return origMaterial(p, flags)
end

local dimage = vgui.GetControlTable("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
local origSetImage = dimage.SetImage
function dimage:SetImage(src, backup)
    if isstring(src) then
        if src:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. savePath, backup)
                elseif backup then
                    origSetImage(self, backup)
                end
            end)
            return
        elseif src:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
            local webPath = src:gsub("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
            local m = lia.webimage.get(webPath)
            if m and not m:IsError() then
                origSetImage(self, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. baseDir .. webPath, backup)
                return
            end
        elseif src:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. baseDir .. webPath, backup)
                return
            end
        else
            local m = lia.webimage.get(src)
            if m and not m:IsError() then
                origSetImage(self, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" .. baseDir .. src, backup)
                return
            end
        end
    end

    origSetImage(self, src, backup)
end

local function findImagesRecursive(dir, result)
    result = result or {}
    local files, dirs = file.Find(dir .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
    if files then
        for _, fn in ipairs(files) do
            table.insert(result, dir .. fn)
        end
    end

    if dirs then
        for _, subdir in ipairs(dirs) do
            findImagesRecursive(dir .. subdir .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", result)
        end
    end
    return result
end

concommand.Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", function()
    local files = findImagesRecursive(baseDir)
    if not files or #files == 0 then return end
    local f = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
    f:SetTitle(L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", f)
    scroll:Dock(FILL)
    local layout = vgui.Create("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", scroll)
    layout:Dock(FILL)
    layout:SetSpaceX(4)
    layout:SetSpaceY(4)
    for _, filePath in ipairs(files) do
        local img = layout:Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
        img:SetMaterial(buildMaterial(filePath))
        img:SetSize(128, 128)
        img:SetTooltip(filePath:sub(#baseDir + 1))
    end
end)

local function deleteDirectoryRecursive(dir)
    local files, dirs = file.Find(dir .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
    if files then
        for _, fn in ipairs(files) do
            file.Delete(dir .. fn)
        end
    end

    if dirs then
        for _, subdir in ipairs(dirs) do
            deleteDirectoryRecursive(dir .. subdir .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
            file.Delete(dir .. subdir)
        end
    end
end

concommand.Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", function()
    local files = findImagesRecursive(baseDir)
    local removedCount = 0
    for _, filePath in ipairs(files) do
        local fileData = file.Read(filePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

")
        if fileData then
            local isValid = false
            if string.lower(string.sub(fileData, 2, 4)) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" then
                isValid = true
            elseif string.lower(string.sub(fileData, 7, 10)) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" or string.lower(string.sub(fileData, 7, 10)) == "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

" then
                isValid = true
            end

            if not isValid then
                file.Delete(filePath)
                removedCount = removedCount + 1
                print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", filePath:sub(#baseDir + 1)))
            end
        else
            file.Delete(filePath)
            removedCount = removedCount + 1
            print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", filePath:sub(#baseDir + 1)))
        end
    end

    for fileName, _ in pairs(cache) do
        local savePath = baseDir .. fileName
        if not file.Exists(savePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

") then
            cache[fileName] = nil
            print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", fileName))
        end
    end

    print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua, gamemode\core\libraries\webimage.lua

", removedCount))
end)

    end)

        img:SetPos(0, 0)
        img:SetSize(imgPanel:GetWide(), imgPanel:GetTall())
        img:SetImage(src)
    end
end)

function lia.webimage.getStats()
    local totalStored = 0
    for _ in pairs(lia.webimage.stored) do
        totalStored = totalStored + 1
    end
    return {
        downloaded = stats.downloaded,
        stored = totalStored,
        lastReset = stats.lastReset
    }
end

"lilia/websounds/"

        if cb then cb(nil, false, L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", name, path)

") then

Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

            if isValid then
                finalize(true)

                finalize(true)
                return
            end

        ensureDir(savePath:match("

        file.Write(savePath, body)
        finalize(false)
    end, function(err)
        if file.Exists(savePath, "

            local existingFileData = file.Read(savePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
            if existingFileData then
                local isValid, cachedValidationError = validateSoundFile(savePath, existingFileData)
                if isValid then
                    finalize(true)
                else
                    file.Delete(savePath)
                    if cb then cb(nil, false, L("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

") then
        local path = buildPath(savePath)
        cache[key] = path
        return path
    end
    return nil
end

local origPlayFile = sound.PlayFile
function sound.PlayFile(path, mode, cb)
    if isstring(path) then
        path = normalizeName(path)
        if path:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", cb)
                return
            end

            lia.websound.register(name, path, function(localPath)
                if localPath then
                    origPlayFile(localPath, mode or "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", cb)
                elseif cb then
                    cb(nil, nil, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
                end
            end)
            return
        else
            local webPath
            if path:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

") then
                webPath = path:gsub("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
            elseif path:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
            else
                webPath = path
            end

            local localPath = lia.websound.get(webPath)
            if localPath then
                if webPath:match("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

") then
                    local reqMode = mode or "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

"
                    local wants3d = reqMode:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", 1, true) ~= nil
                    local attempts = {}
                    local seen = {}
                    local function add(m)
                        if m and m ~= "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

" and not seen[m] then
                            seen[m] = true
                            table.insert(attempts, m)
                        end
                    end

                    if wants3d then
                        add(reqMode)
                        add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
                        add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
                    else
                        add(reqMode)
                        table.insert(attempts, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
                    end

                    local function tryNext(i, lastErrCode, lastErrStr)
                        local m = attempts[i]
                        if not m then
                            if cb then cb(nil, lastErrCode, lastErrStr or "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

") end
                            return
                        end

                        origPlayFile(localPath, m, function(ch, errCode, errStr)
                            if IsValid(ch) then
                                if cb then cb(ch, errCode, errStr) end
                            else
                                tryNext(i + 1, errCode, errStr)
                            end
                        end)
                    end

                    tryNext(1)
                    return
                else
                    return origPlayFile(localPath, mode or "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", cb)
                end
            end
        end
    end
    return origPlayFile(path, mode, cb)
end

local origPlayURL = sound.PlayURL
function sound.PlayURL(url, mode, cb)
    if isstring(url) and url:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

"
        if reqMode:find("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", 1, true) ~= nil then
            origPlayURL(url, reqMode, cb)
            local name = urlMap[url]
            if not name then
                name = deriveUrlSaveName(url)
                urlMap[url] = name
            end

            lia.websound.register(name, url)
            return
        end

        local name = urlMap[url]
        if not name then
            name = deriveUrlSaveName(url)
            urlMap[url] = name
        end

        local cachedPath = lia.websound.get(name)
        if cachedPath then
            origPlayFile(cachedPath, mode or "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", cb)
            return
        end

        lia.websound.register(name, url, function(localPath)
            if localPath then
                origPlayFile(localPath, mode or "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", cb)
            elseif cb then
                cb(nil, nil, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
            end
        end)
        return
    end
    return origPlayURL(url, mode, cb)
end

concommand.Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

    local files = file.Find(baseDir .. "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
    if not files or #files == 0 then return end
    local f = vgui.Create("

    layout:Dock(FILL)

    layout:SetSpaceY(4)
    for _, fn in ipairs(files) do
        local btn = layout:Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

        btn:SetText(fn)
        btn:SetSize(200, 20)
        btn.DoClick = function() sound.PlayFile(buildPath(baseDir .. fn), "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", function(chan) if chan then chan:Play() end end) end
    end
end)

concommand.Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
    for _, fn in ipairs(files) do
        file.Delete(baseDir .. fn)
    end

    cache = {}
    urlMap = {}
    MsgC(Color(83, 143, 239), "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", Color(0, 255, 0), "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
    local validCount = 0
    local invalidCount = 0
    local corruptedFiles = {}
    for _, fileName in ipairs(files) do
        local filePath = baseDir .. fileName
        local fileData = file.Read(filePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
        if fileData then
            local isValid, errorMsg = validateSoundFile(fileName, fileData)
            if isValid then
                validCount = validCount + 1
            else
                invalidCount = invalidCount + 1
                table.insert(corruptedFiles, fileName)
                print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", fileName, errorMsg))
            end
        else
            invalidCount = invalidCount + 1
            table.insert(corruptedFiles, fileName)
            print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", validCount, invalidCount))
    if #corruptedFiles > 0 then
        for _, fileName in ipairs(corruptedFiles) do
            print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", fileName))
        end
    end
end)

concommand.Add("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
    local removedCount = 0
    for _, fileName in ipairs(files) do
        local filePath = baseDir .. fileName
        local fileData = file.Read(filePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
        if fileData then
            local isValid, errorMsg = validateSoundFile(fileName, fileData)
            if not isValid then
                file.Delete(filePath)
                removedCount = removedCount + 1
                print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", fileName, errorMsg))
            end
        else
            file.Delete(filePath)
            removedCount = removedCount + 1
            print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", fileName))
        end
    end

    for fileName, _ in pairs(cache) do
        local savePath = baseDir .. fileName
        if not file.Exists(savePath, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
    if #files == 0 then return end
    for _, fileName in ipairs(files) do
        local fileSize = file.Size(baseDir .. fileName, "
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

")
        print(string.format("
Files: gamemode\core\libraries\websound.lua

", fileName, fileSize))
    end
end)
